sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Kueue Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as Kueue Controller<br/>(watch via K8s API)
    participant Scheduler as Kueue Scheduler<br/>(in-process)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User, Scheduler: Flow 1: Job Admission

    User->>K8sAPI: Submit Job (e.g., PyTorchJob)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / Client Cert
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-*<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: API Server TLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Job (queue label injected)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-*<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: API Server TLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result

    Note over Controller: Watch event received

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Job CRs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Job Event (Created)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Workload CR<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Scheduler: Scheduling cycle

    Scheduler->>Scheduler: Check ClusterQueue quota<br/>Evaluate priorities<br/>Fair-sharing policies
    Scheduler->>Controller: Admit Workload (in-process)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Workload status (Admitted)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Unsuspend Job / Create Pods<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Prometheus, Controller: Flow 2: Metrics Scraping

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Auth Result
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Metrics Response
